%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=dedf94a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n睇消息去實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=05e479e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n不要說推<br />\n試著說812機場見"},{"pid":"5741c17092c750bb3e1086287ee743163498c338","tid":1450352,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:35:20.000Z","msg":"見到在場有人帶古怪豬姐，有濾棉但係冇濾罐，甚至有人濾棉都冇，得個豬姐<br />\n<br />\n呢個今日尖沙咀都有 <br />\n我都諗緊佢做乜鳩<br />\n原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9f88ebb53d2e70221446f6b7df5d66e7a98a67","tid":1450352,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c79fc336fde083992d522b61ea8bd2ac03c51c0d","tid":1450352,"uid":34779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"黑警我屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538c29a0d13fe3ce926888a2114f8e73e20dfff3","tid":1450352,"uid":273991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:44:34.000Z","msg":"有用推"},{"pid":"f84aa4474e77ecc3710f3988df6e1efed2d4edfa","tid":1450352,"uid":31690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:49:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10515967d366e50a40288685f1654e51d5ae17f5","tid":1450352,"uid":269428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:51:57.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4ac344c778a6c36c20f5500f8d869ddb8